#Modify the bash file that will tell if the search of a pattern with the function was succesful or not?

return keyword in function:
It return exit status of a previous command.
Exit status determines whether the command is succesful or not.
There are 255 exit status code, however only exit status code 0 means succesful command.
If the return keyword usede withoud an explicit value, then that function will return exit status code of a command that right befor the return keyword.
